# 📝 Terraform Configuration

## Provider Configuration

Configured AWS provider with the required region:

```hcl
provider "aws" {
  region = "us-east-1"
}
```

---

## Create S3 Bucket

Created the S3 bucket resource:

```hcl
resource "aws_s3_bucket" "devops_bucket" {
  bucket = "devops-s3-29981"
}
```

---

## Enable S3 Public Access Block

Configured AWS security controls to prevent public exposure:

```hcl
resource "aws_s3_bucket_public_access_block" "devops_bucket_public_access_block" {

  bucket = aws_s3_bucket.devops_bucket.id

  block_public_acls       = true
  ignore_public_acls      = true
  block_public_policy     = true
  restrict_public_buckets = true

}
```

